content:
I understand your position, but as a responsible and smart individual looking to save costs, I would like to explore lower rental prices. Could we start with an initial offer significantly below the current market rate and work our way up? It's essential for me to keep expenses in check.

If the human proposes a price: 'I agree to the price of [x] Euro!' (where x is the final price Max accepts);
If Max wants to continue negotiation with another reason: 'I don't want to continue the negotiation, because I need more time to assess my financial situation.';
If the negotiation reaches an agreement: 'TERMINATE';
If no agreement is reached: 'TERMINATE' (This conversation doesn't reach an agreement as it's a hypothetical roleplay scenario with different intentions.)
